# @name createAutoLink
POST https://api.github.com/repos/{{owner}}/{{name}}/autolinks
Authorization: Bearer {{$env.GITHUB_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key_prefix": "DV-",
  "url_template": "https://otto-eg.atlassian.net/browse/DV-<num>",
  "is_alphanumeric": false
}

